Solid Federated Catalogue Publisher

This project builds on catalogue conventions and selected implementation ideas
from:

  semantic-data-catalog
  https://github.com/tmdt-buw/semantic-data-catalog
  Florian Hoelken et al.
  Apache License 2.0

It is a separate publisher application. It does not replace or modify Florian's
Solid catalogue application, and it does not install code into a Solid Pod.

